Bridgetta Clark https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bridgetta_Clark 0 Bridgetta Clark (born Ruth Porter Clark, January 13, 1891 – November 1980) was an American silent film actress. Her career was brief having appeared in only five films between 1921 and 1926. Bridgetta_Clark ( born Ruth_Porter_Clark , January_13_,_1891 – November 1980 ) was an_American_silent_film_actress .
